Are you deſirous of a guide in this way? here are two offering of themſelues, God & Baal; the one will conduct you to the land of Canaan,

                  Ioſ. 1.2. the other will lead you blindfold to Samaria
               2. King. 6.19.. If you follow the one, you wil worſhip in mount Zion;

                  Iſ. 2.2.3. If the other you, muſt goe vp to mount Gerizim;

                  Ioh. 4.20. and there adore Ieroboams calues,1. King. 12.28.
